        regression test. 769 unit tests in <code>cargo test --lib</code>,
        +23 added during the audit. Clippy <code>-D warnings</code>
        clean. Bug-by-bug write-up in
        <a href="https://github.com/beshu-tech/deltaglider_proxy/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">CHANGELOG.md</a>.
