      <h2>Get started</h2>

      <pre><code>docker run -p 9000:9000 \
  -e DGP_BACKEND=s3 \
  -e DGP_S3_ENDPOINT=https://your-backend \
  -e AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=... \
  -e AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=... \
  ghcr.io/beshu-tech/deltaglider_proxy:latest</code></pre>

